iv>\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-on-surface-variant\">Expedite Adjustment</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\" id=\"deliveryFee\">¥120</span></div>\n<div class=\"h-px bg-outline-variant\"></div>\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-on-surface-variant\">Quantity</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\" id=\"summaryQuantity\">20 pcs</span></div>\n<div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\"><span class=\"text-on-surface-variant\">Notes</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface text-right\" id=\"summaryRemarks\">Estimated by default with 5-axis milling</span></div>\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-primary/5 px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between\">\n<span class=\"text-[13px] font-bold text-on-surface\">Estimated Total</span>\n<span class=\"text-[18px] font-bold text-primary\" id=\"quoteTotal\">¥7,080</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest p-4 shadow-sm\">\n<h5 class=\"text-body-sm font-bold text-on-surface\">Order Settings</h5>\n<div class=\"mt-4 space-y-4\">\n<label class=\"block\">\n<span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Quantity</span>\n<input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"quoteQuantityInput\" min=\"1\" type=\"number\" value=\"20\"/>\n</label>\n<label class=\"block\">\n<span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Lead Time</span>\n<select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"quoteDeliverySelect\">\n<option value=\"7 days\">7 days</option>\n<option selected=\"\" value=\"10 days\">10 days</option>\n<option value=\"15 days\">15 days</option>\n<option value=\"21 days\">21 days</option>\n</select>\n</label>\n<label class=\"block\">\n<span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">Notes</span>\n<textarea class=\"min-h-[88px] w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"quoteRemarksInput\" placeholder=\"Add volume, inspection, and delivery notes\">Estimated by default with 5-axis milling</textarea>\n</label>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low p-4 shadow-sm\" id=\"serviceStatusCard\">\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n<div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">support_agent</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"min-w-0\">\n<p class=\"text-body-sm font-bold text-on-surface\" id=\"serviceStatusTitle\">Service Status</p>\n<p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant\" id=\"serviceStatusText\">The current mode is AI intelligent quoting. You can place the order directly, or switch to customer service follow-up or manual quoting.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"p-4 border-t border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest space-y-2\">\n<button class=\"w-full rounded-xl bg-primary px-4 py-3 text-body-sm font-bold text-on-primary hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity\" type=\"button\">Quick Order</button>\n<button class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-4 py-3 text-body-sm font-bold text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors\" type=\"button\">Submit Order</button>\n<button class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-4 py-3 text-body-sm font-bold text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors\" data-service-followup=\"\" type=\"button\">Customer Service Follow-up</button>\n<button class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5 px-4 py-3 text-body-sm font-bold text-primary hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors\" data-service-manual=\"\" type=\"button\">Transfer to Manual Quote</button>\n</div>\n</aside>"
